  "texts": [
    "This might cause oscillations at the edge of the safe space, leading to system instability.",
    "Additionally, the robot might get stuck in a local minimum and never accomplish the task [21].",
    "The next section proposes an approach to improve the post-posed shield design.",
    "V. PREDICTIVE SAFETY SHIELD BASED ONDYNA-Q-LEARNING Contrary to many existing approaches, when the safety shield interrupts the agent only when it is about to take an unsafe action, we propose interrupting the agent if it takes an action that is verified unsafe in the next N steps.",
    "We then use a model of the world to simulate the two-player game, where the agent tries to maximize its reward, and the safety shield acts as a controversial agent."
